edu.neu.coe.info6205.life.base

Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.neu.coe.info6205.life.base.Group
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Countable, Renderable

    public class Group
extends java.lang.Object
implements Renderable, Countable
    Class to model a group of cells. Groups may not overlap. If an overlap occurs through expansion, then the groups must merge.
